{"title_page": "Catacombe (film)", "text_new": "{{short description|2018 film}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Catacombe\n| image          = Catacombe poster.jpg\n| caption        = Film poster\n| director       = [[Victor D. Ponten]]\n| producer       = \n| writer         = Victor D. Ponten\n| starring       = [[The Opposites|Willem de Bruin]]<br>[[Kevin Janssens (actor)|Kevin Janssens]]\n| music          = \n| cinematography = \n| editing        = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{film date|2018|9|18|df=yes}}\n| runtime        = \n| country        = Netherlands\n| language       = Dutch\n| budget         = \n}}\n\n'''''Catacombe''''' is a 2018 Dutch [[drama film]] directed by [[Victor D. Ponten]].<ref name=\"HFN\">{{cite web |url=https://www.hollandfilmnieuws.nl/nieuwscategorieen/in-productie/willem-de-bruin-speelt-hoofdrol-in-catacombe/ |title=Willem de Bruin speelt hoofdrol in Catacombe |work=Holland Film Nieuws |accessdate=21 July 2018}}</ref> In July 2018, it was one of nine films shortlisted to be the Dutch entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[91st Academy Awards]], but it was not selected.<ref name=\"Eye\">{{cite web |url=https://international.eyefilm.nl/feature-film.html |title=Feature Film Academy Entry |work=EYE Film Institute Netherlands |date=20 July 2018 |accessdate=21 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[The Opposites|Willem de Bruin]] as Jermaine Slagter\n* [[Kevin Janssens (actor)|Kevin Janssens]] as Kevin van Looy\n* [[Orion Lee]] as Charlie Yuen\n* [[Werner Kolf]] as Samuel\n* [[Liliana de Vries]] as Naomi\n* [[Loes Schnepper]] as Coby\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|6438398|Catacombe}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Catacombe}}\n[[Category:2018 films]]\n[[Category:2010s drama films]]\n[[Category:Dutch films]]\n[[Category:Dutch drama films]]\n[[Category:Dutch-language films]]\n{{Netherlands-film-stub}}\n{{2010s-drama-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2018 film}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2018}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Catacombe\n| image          = Catacombe poster.jpg\n| caption        = Film poster\n| director       = [[Victor D. Ponten]]\n| producer       = \n| writer         = Victor D. Ponten\n| starring       = [[The Opposites|Willem de Bruin]]<br>[[Kevin Janssens (actor)|Kevin Janssens]]\n| music          = \n| cinematography = \n| editing        = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = {{film date|2018|9|18|df=yes}}\n| runtime        = \n| country        = Netherlands\n| language       = Dutch\n| budget         = \n}}\n\n'''''Catacombe''''' is a 2018 Dutch [[drama film]] directed by [[Victor D. Ponten]].<ref name=\"HFN\">{{cite web |url=https://www.hollandfilmnieuws.nl/nieuwscategorieen/in-productie/willem-de-bruin-speelt-hoofdrol-in-catacombe/ |title=Willem de Bruin speelt hoofdrol in Catacombe |work=Holland Film Nieuws |accessdate=21 July 2018}}</ref> In July 2018, it was one of nine films shortlisted to be the Dutch entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[91st Academy Awards]], but it was not selected.<ref name=\"Eye\">{{cite web |url=https://international.eyefilm.nl/feature-film.html |title=Feature Film Academy Entry |work=EYE Film Institute Netherlands |date=20 July 2018 |accessdate=21 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[The Opposites|Willem de Bruin]] as Jermaine Slagter\n* [[Kevin Janssens (actor)|Kevin Janssens]] as Kevin van Looy\n* [[Orion Lee]] as Charlie Yuen\n* [[Werner Kolf]] as Samuel\n* [[Liliana de Vries]] as Naomi\n* [[Loes Schnepper]] as Coby\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|6438398|Catacombe}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Catacombe}}\n[[Category:2018 films]]\n[[Category:2010s drama films]]\n[[Category:Dutch films]]\n[[Category:Dutch drama films]]\n[[Category:Dutch-language films]]\n{{Netherlands-film-stub}}\n{{2010s-drama-film-stub}}\n", "n